---
import MainLayout from '../layouts/MainLayout.astro';
---

<MainLayout title="Escríbenos - Soluciones Logísticas | Grupo Transporte RG">
    
    <section class="relative w-full pt-40 pb-20 md:pt-48 md:pb-28 px-6 md:px-12 overflow-hidden bg-zinc-900">
    
        <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-cover bg-center transition-transform duration-[10s] hover:scale-105 opacity-80"
            style="background-image: url('/img/contact-hero.jpg');">
        </div>
        
        <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-t from-zinc-50 dark:from-zinc-950 via-black/40 to-transparent z-0"></div>

        <div class="relative z-10 max-w-4xl mx-auto text-center flex flex-col items-center">
            <div class="inline-flex items-center px-4 py-1.5 rounded-full text-xs font-bold uppercase bg-[#f0ba18] text-black mb-6 shadow-[0_0_15px_rgba(240,186,24,0.4)] animate-fade-up">
                <i class="fas fa-headset mr-2"></i> Estamos para ayudarte
            </div>

            <h1 class="font-brand text-5xl md:text-7xl text-white font-bold leading-tight animate-fade-up uppercase tracking-wide drop-shadow-2xl" style="animation-delay: 0.1s;">
                Ponte en <br class="md:hidden"> <span class="text-[#f0ba18] drop-shadow-md">Contacto</span>
            </h1>

            <p class="text-white text-lg md:text-xl font-medium leading-relaxed mt-6 max-w-2xl animate-fade-up drop-shadow-md" style="animation-delay: 0.2s;">
                ¿Tienes dudas sobre nuestros servicios o deseas una cotización? Nuestro equipo está listo para brindarte la mejor asesoría personalizada.
            </p>
        </div>
    </section>

    <div class="w-full bg-zinc-50 dark:bg-zinc-950 transition-colors duration-500 pb-24">
        
        <div class="relative z-30 flex justify-center -mt-8 mb-16 animate-fade-up" style="animation-delay: 0.25s;">
            <div class="bg-white dark:bg-zinc-900 p-2 rounded-full shadow-xl border border-gray-100 dark:border-zinc-800 flex space-x-2 sm:space-x-4">
                <a href="https://wa.me/573225019305?text=Vengo%20desde%20la%20web,%20quisiera%20saber%20mas%20informacion%20sobre%20sus%20servicios." target="_blank" class="px-6 py-2.5 rounded-full bg-[#f0ba18] text-black font-bold hover:bg-yellow-400 transition-all text-sm md:text-base shadow-md">
                    <i class="fab fa-whatsapp text-lg mr-2"></i> Escríbenos
                </a>
                <a href="/contacto/faq" class="px-6 py-2.5 rounded-full text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-300 hover:bg-gray-100 dark:hover:bg-zinc-800 font-bold transition-all text-sm md:text-base">
                    <i class="fas fa-question-circle mr-2"></i> Preguntas Frecuentes
                </a>
            </div>
        </div>
        
        <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-6 relative z-20">
            
            <div class="flex flex-wrap justify-center gap-8 mb-16">
                
                <a href="tel:+573225019305" class="group flex flex-col items-center text-center bg-white dark:bg-zinc-900 rounded-3xl p-10 shadow-lg hover:shadow-2xl transition-all duration-500 border border-gray-100 dark:border-zinc-800 hover:border-[#f0ba18] w-full md:w-[calc(50%-1rem)] lg:w-[calc(33.33%-1.5rem)] max-w-sm animate-fade-up cursor-pointer" style="animation-delay: 0.3s;">
                    <div class="w-20 h-20 rounded-full bg-[#f0ba18]/10 text-[#f0ba18] flex items-center justify-center mb-6 group-hover:scale-110 transition-transform duration-300">
                        <i class="fas fa-phone-alt text-3xl"></i>
                    </div>
                    <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-3 text-black dark:text-white">Hablemos</h3>
                    <p class="text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-400 mb-2 text-lg">Línea Nacional:</p>
                    <p class="text-[#f0ba18] font-bold text-xl mb-6">(+57) 322 5019305</p>
                    
                    <div class="mt-auto pt-6 border-t border-gray-100 dark:border-zinc-800 w-full">
                        <p class="text-sm text-[#f0ba18] font-bold">
                            <i class="fas fa-mobile-alt mr-1"></i> Clic aquí para llamar
                        </p>
                    </div>
                </a>

                <a href="mailto:contacto@grupotransporterg.com" class="group flex flex-col items-center text-center bg-white dark:bg-zinc-900 rounded-3xl p-10 shadow-lg hover:shadow-2xl transition-all duration-500 border border-gray-100 dark:border-zinc-800 hover:border-[#f0ba18] w-full md:w-[calc(50%-1rem)] lg:w-[calc(33.33%-1.5rem)] max-w-sm animate-fade-up cursor-pointer" style="animation-delay: 0.4s;">
                    <div class="w-20 h-20 rounded-full bg-[#f0ba18]/10 text-[#f0ba18] flex items-center justify-center mb-6 group-hover:scale-110 transition-transform duration-300">
                        <i class="fas fa-envelope text-3xl"></i>
                    </div>
                    <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-3 text-black dark:text-white">Envía un Correo</h3>
                    <p class="text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-400 mb-2 text-lg">Atención comercial:</p>
                    <p class="text-[#f0ba18] font-bold text-base md:text-lg mb-6 break-all">contacto@grupotransporterg.com</p>
                    
                    <div class="mt-auto pt-6 border-t border-gray-100 dark:border-zinc-800 w-full">
                        <p class="text-sm text-[#f0ba18] font-bold">
                            <i class="fas fa-paper-plane mr-1"></i> Clic para redactar
                        </p>
                    </div>
                </a>

                <a href="https://maps.google.com/?q=Grupo+Transporte+RG,+Calle+12+%234-34,+La+Virginia,+Risaralda,+Colombia" target="_blank" class="group flex flex-col items-center text-center bg-white dark:bg-zinc-900 rounded-3xl p-10 shadow-lg hover:shadow-2xl transition-all duration-500 border border-gray-100 dark:border-zinc-800 hover:border-[#f0ba18] w-full md:w-[calc(50%-1rem)] lg:w-[calc(33.33%-1.5rem)] max-w-sm animate-fade-up cursor-pointer" style="animation-delay: 0.5s;">
                    <div class="w-20 h-20 rounded-full bg-[#f0ba18]/10 text-[#f0ba18] flex items-center justify-center mb-6 group-hover:scale-110 transition-transform duration-300">
                        <i class="fas fa-map-marker-alt text-3xl"></i>
                    </div>
                    <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-3 text-black dark:text-white">Sede Principal</h3>
                    <p class="text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-400 mb-6 text-lg font-light">Oficina Grupo Transporte RG<br>Calle 12 #4-34, La Virginia</p>
                    
                    <div class="mt-auto pt-6 border-t border-gray-100 dark:border-zinc-800 w-full">
                        <p class="text-sm text-[#f0ba18] font-bold">
                            <i class="fas fa-map mr-1"></i> Clic para abrir en la App
                        </p>
                    </div>
                </a>

            </div>

            <div class="flex flex-col lg:flex-row bg-white dark:bg-zinc-900 rounded-[2rem] shadow-xl overflow-hidden border border-gray-100 dark:border-zinc-800 animate-fade-up group" style="animation-delay: 0.6s;">
                
                <div class="w-full lg:w-5/12 p-10 lg:p-14 flex flex-col justify-center relative z-20 bg-white dark:bg-zinc-900">
                    <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-extrabold text-black dark:text-white mb-6 leading-tight">
                        Contáctanos para recibir <span class="text-[#f0ba18]">más información</span>
                    </h2>
                    
                    <p class="text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-400 mb-10 text-lg leading-relaxed">
                        Comunícate con nuestro equipo especializado. Recibe asesoría personalizada en servicios de transporte, logística y distribución a nivel nacional.
                    </p>
                    
                    <div class="inline-flex">
                        <a href="https://wa.me/573225019305?text=Vengo%20desde%20la%20web,%20quisiera%20saber%20mas%20informacion%20sobre%20sus%20servicios." target="_blank" 
                           class="inline-flex items-center bg-black dark:bg-zinc-800 text-white font-bold text-lg px-8 py-4 rounded-xl transition-all duration-300 transform hover:-translate-y-1 hover:bg-[#f0ba18] hover:text-black shadow-lg">
                            ¡Cotiza Ahora!
                            <i class="fab fa-whatsapp ml-3 text-xl"></i>
                        </a>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <div class="w-full lg:w-7/12 min-h-[400px] lg:min-h-full relative bg-gray-200 dark:bg-zinc-800">
                    
                    <a href="https://maps.google.com/?q=Grupo+Transporte+RG,+Calle+12+%234-34,+La+Virginia,+Risaralda,+Colombia" 
                       target="_blank" 
                       class="absolute inset-0 z-10 block md:hidden cursor-pointer"
                       aria-label="Abrir ubicación en Google Maps">
                    </a>

                    <iframe 
                        src="https://maps.google.com/maps?q=Grupo+Transporte+RG,+Calle+12+%234-34,+La+Virginia,+Risaralda&t=&z=16&ie=UTF8&iwloc=&output=embed"
                        class="absolute inset-0 w-full h-full border-0 pointer-events-none md:pointer-events-auto" 
                        allowfullscreen="" 
                        loading="lazy"
                        referrerpolicy="no-referrer-when-downgrade">
                    </iframe>

                    <a href="https://maps.google.com/?q=Grupo+Transporte+RG,+Calle+12+%234-34,+La+Virginia,+Risaralda,+Colombia" 
                       target="_blank" 
                       class="absolute bottom-6 right-6 z-20 bg-white dark:bg-zinc-900 text-black dark:text-white px-5 py-3 rounded-2xl shadow-2xl font-bold flex items-center border border-gray-100 dark:border-zinc-800 hover:bg-[#f0ba18] hover:text-black transition-all transform hover:-translate-y-1">
                        <i class="fas fa-external-link-alt text-[#f0ba18] group-hover:text-black mr-2 transition-colors"></i> 
                        Abrir en Google Maps
                    </a>

                </div>
            </div>
        </div>

    </div>
</MainLayout>

<style>
    html {
        scroll-behavior: smooth;
    }

    .animate-fade-up {
        animation: fadeUp 0.8s ease-out forwards;
        opacity: 0;
        transform: translateY(20px);
    }

    @keyframes fadeUp {
        to { opacity: 1; transform: translateY(0); }
    }
</style>